templateDeclaration xmlns:imsqti="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqti_v2p1" identifier="a" cardinality="single" baseType="integer" /><imsqti:templateDeclaration xmlns:imsqti="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqti_v2p1" identifier="b" cardinality="single" baseType="integer" /><imsqti:templateDeclaration xmlns:imsqti="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqti_v2p1" identifier="c" cardinality="single" baseType="integer" /><imsqti:templateDeclaration xmlns:imsqti="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqti_v2p1" identifier="d" cardinality="single" baseType="integer" /><imsqti:templateDeclaration xmlns:imsqti="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqti_v2p1" identifier="f" cardinality="single" baseType="integer" /><imsqti:templateDeclaration xmlns:imsqti="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqti_v2p1" identifier="f+1" cardinality="single" baseType="integer" /><imsqti:templateProcessing xmlns:imsqti="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqti_v2p1"><imsqti:setTemplateValue identifier="var1"><imsqti:randomInteger min="1" max="10" /></imsqti:setTemplateValue><imsqti:setTemplateValue identifier="var2"><imsqti:randomInteger min="1" max="10" /></imsqti:setTemplateValue><imsqti:setTemplateValue identifier="solution"><imsqti:customOperator definition="MAXIMA" value="float($(1)+$(2));"><imsqti:variable identifier="var1" /><imsqti:variable identifier="var2" /></imsqti:customOperator></imsqti:setTemplateValue><imsqti:setTemplateValue identifier="a"><imsqti:randomInteger min="1" max="5" /></imsqti:setTemplateValue><imsqti:setTemplateValue identifier="b"><imsqti:randomInteger min="1" max="6" /></imsqti:setTemplateValue><imsqti:setTemplateValue identifier="c"><imsqti:randomInteger min="1" max="7" /></imsqti:setTemplateValue><imsqti:setTemplateValue identifier="d"><imsqti:randomInteger min="1" max="7" /></imsqti:setTemplateValue><imsqti:setTemplateValue identifier="f"><imsqti:randomInteger min="2" max="8" /></imsqti:setTemplateValue><imsqti:setTemplateValue identifier="f+1"><imsqti:customOperator definition="MAXIMA" value="float($(1)+1);"><imsqti:variable identifier="f" /></imsqti:customOperator></imsqti:setTemplateValue><imsqti:setCorrectResponse identifier="RESPONSE_1414667120916"><imsqti:customOperator definition="VARIABLESTRING" value="($(1)-$(2)*%i)*(k+1)/(k+$(3))"><imsqti:variable identifier="a" /><imsqti:variable identifier="b" /><imsqti:variable identifier="f+1" /></imsqti:customOperator></imsqti:setCorrectResponse></imsqti:templateProcessing><itemBody ><p>Consider the power series:</p><p>$$ f(z ) = \sum_{k=0}^{\infty} \frac{<printedVariable identifier="a" />- <printedVariable identifier="b" /> \cdot \bf{i}}{(k+<printedVariable identifier="f" />)} ( z - <printedVariable identifier="c" /> + <printedVariable identifier="d" /> \dot \bf{i})^{k} $$.</p><p>Compute the first derivative of f within its disc of convergence, that is,</p><p>$$ f'(z ) = \sum_{k=0}^{\infty} b_k ( z - <printedVariable identifier="c" /> + <printedVariable identifier="d" /> \dot \bf{i})^k $$ with \( b_k \in \mathbb C\) for each \( k \in \mathbb N_0 \):</p><p>Enter the term \( b_k\) depending on k. Use %i for the imaginary unit i and * for any multiplikation.</p><p><strong>Note that both power series (f and f') start at the index k = 0.</strong></p><p>Example of correct input syntax: For the term \( \frac{2-3\dot i}{k^2} \) you enter (2- 3*%i)/k^2</p><p>\( b_k \) = <textEntryInteraction responseIdentifier="RESPONSE_1414667120916" expectedLength="15" class="maxima-formula show-latex show-syntax-error" />, \( k \in \mathbb N_0 \)</p><p> </p><p> </p><p> </p></itemBody><imsqti:responseProcessing xmlns:imsqti="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqti_v2p1"><imsqti:responseCondition><imsqti:responseIf><imsqti:customOperator definition="MAXIMA" value="is(equal(ev($(1)),ev($(2))));"><imsqti:variable identifier="RESPONSE_1414667120916" /><imsqti:correct identifier="RESPONSE_1414667120916" /></imsqti:customOperator><imsqti:setOutcomeValue identifier="SCORE"><imsqti:sum><imsqti:variable identifier="SCORE" /><imsqti:baseValue baseType="float">2</imsqti:baseValue></imsqti:sum></imsqti:setOutcomeValue></imsqti:responseIf></imsqti:responseCondition><imsqti:responseCondition><imsqti:responseIf><imsqti:not><imsqti:isNull><imsqti:variable identifier="RESPONSE_1414667120916" /></imsqti:isNull></imsqti:not><imsqti:setOutcomeValue identifier="FEEDBACKBASIC"><imsqti:baseValue baseType="identifier">incorrect</imsqti:baseValue></imsqti:setOutcomeValue></imsqti:responseIf></imsqti:responseCondition><imsqti:responseCondition><imsqti:responseIf><imsqti:and><imsqti:not><imsqti:match><imsqti:variable identifier="FEEDBACKBASIC" /><imsqti:baseValue baseType="identifier">empty</imsqti:baseValue></imsqti:match></imsqti:not><imsqti:equal toleranceMode="exact"><imsqti:variable identifier="SCORE" /><imsqti:variable identifier="MAXSCORE" /></imsqti:equal></imsqti:and><imsqti:setOutcomeValue identifier="FEEDBACKBASIC"><imsqti:baseValue baseType="identifier">correct</imsqti:baseValue></imsqti:setOutcomeValue></imsqti:responseIf></imsqti:responseCondition><imsqti:responseCondition><imsqti:responseIf><imsqti:and><imsqti:match><imsqti:baseValue baseType="identifier">incorrect</imsqti:baseValue><imsqti:variable identifier="FEEDBACKBASIC" /></imsqti:match></imsqti:and><imsqti:setOutcomeValue identifier="FEEDBACKMODAL"><imsqti:multiple><imsqti:variable identifier="FEEDBACKMODAL" /><imsqti:baseValue baseType="identifier">Feedback117336600</imsqti:baseValue></imsqti:multiple></imsqti:setOutcomeValue></imsqti:responseIf></imsqti:responseCondition></imsqti:responseProcessing><modalFeedback  identifier="Feedback117336600" outcomeIdentifier="FEEDBACKMODAL" showHide="show"><p>Let \( f(z) =  \sum_{k=0}^{\infty} a_k \cdot z^k \) be a power series. Then</p><p>\( f'(z) =  \sum_{k=0}^{\infty} a_k \cdot k \cdot z^{k-1} = \sum_{k=1}^{\infty} a_k \cdot k \cdot z^{k-1}\) because the first term is zero. Now shift the index k back to zero and you get:</p><p>\( f'(z) = \sum_{k=0}^{\infty} a_{k+1} \cdot (k+1) \cdot z^k \).</p></modalFeedback></assessmentItem>
